We cordially invite you to our conference "Capitalism of the Future", which will take place on 4 November in Prague. Join us for discussions on today's key socio-economic issues such as environmentalism, digitalisation, migration and social justice in the context of today's capitalism and the capitalism of the future.

Is the only way to protect nature not to grow? Or is a free market enough? Can only the state digitize? And haven't private companies been doing it themselves for years? What is the most effective way to eradicate poverty? By opening up borders!

Come and listen to lectures on these and many other topics by Czech and international speakers on 4 November and then discuss them with us. The exact location of the conference will be announced soon.
